            <a href="http://www.hispanicfund.org/">Hispanic Fund</a> - Promoter of Hispanic Higher Education Support and Assistance
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <a href="http://www.greatmindsinstem.org/college/henaac-scholarship-program">HENNAC Scholars</a> - Recognition of underserved scholars and provide scholarship programs
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h5>Careers</h5>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>
            <a href="http://www.aftercollege.com/group/354032134/">After College</a> - An indispensable tool for SHPE employment
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <a href="http://www.careercenter.uiuc.edu/interestgroups/default.asp">Career Center</a> - Professional services including resume tuning, mock interviews and more
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span8 offset2">
      <h3 class="text-center">Additional Help</h3>
      <p>
        Can't find what you're looking for? Send a message to the <a href="mailto:advisor@shpe-uiuc.org">student advisor</a> and he/she will get back to you as soon as possible.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
